## Data Transformation

All API responses are transformed using `src/services/api/transformers.ts`:
- ✅ `GraphData` - Nodes and edges transformed to frontend format
- ✅ `CompanyDetail` - Chart data points transformed
- ✅ `StockEvent` - Events transformed (content field ignored)
- ⚠️ Missing fields generated where possible (`history`, `name`, `price`, etc.)

## Environment Variables

- `VITE_API_BASE_URL` - Backend API base URL (defaults: localhost:3000 dev, graphfolio-backend.onrender.com prod)
- `VITE_USE_MOCKS` - Force mock mode (set to 'true' to disable API calls)

## Validation

Run `npm run validate:api` to test all endpoints and validate responses.

**Legend:**
- ✅ Implemented: Real API call implemented with transformation and validation
- ⚠️ Partial: API call implemented but schema incomplete or missing fields
- ⚠️ Fallback: Endpoint not in OpenAPI spec, using mock data
